{"tid":330037,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全運會項目增設大媽廣場舞","createTime":"2017-07-21T00:13:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-21T17:54:56.000Z","uid":37554,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"cf65a9326cebfbaeeed465e40e2e0fed84daa347","tid":330037,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T00:13:07.000Z","msg":"大媽舞都變運動項目？唔係同你講笑，呢隻所謂嘅廣場舞，已被列入第13屆中國全運會比賽項目中。<br />\n<br />\n據《中國新聞網》記者由「我要上全運」全民健身網絡競賽活動的新聞發佈會上，得悉呢個消息，仲話廣場舞係舞蹈藝術中最龐大嘅系統，呢種因在廣場聚集而得名、將自娛同表演融為一體嘅舞蹈，已經逐漸成為最受民眾歡迎嘅一種休閑娛樂健身活動，現在被納入比賽項目，證明官方對呢種舞蹈嘅肯定。<br />\n報道又話50多年歷史嘅全運會，近年隨住國家體育改革，功能同價值觀一直改變緊，希望可以有多元發掘及展現，增設更多群眾可以參與嘅項目，好似今年就19個項目開設群眾性嘅比賽，包括馬拉松、羽毛球、國際跳棋及乒乓球等，而大媽舞亦喺呢種背景下應運而生。"},{"pid":"554c20f48ce22915d77d5e9e29d1fde3c854ce76","tid":330037,"uid":37554,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T00:13:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170721/large/1500575149_1714.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170721%2Flarge%2F1500575149_1714.jpg&h=e407ba04&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1b718745dc34dcf71a29c11d6d3966174b0cf0ab","tid":330037,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T00:16:36.000Z","msg":"on撚9"},{"pid":"6923781d975f4599ca8ffb230e69af1140f8cbd0","tid":330037,"uid":42374,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T00:18:20.000Z","msg":"屌係咪on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97b3c458a485da6dba1b1b0bda371a7322afe7d5","tid":330037,"uid":48796,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T00:29:58.000Z","msg":"支那人冇taste可言"},{"pid":"4358800bba93facff2aeb4d72ea9d5838cbd1585","tid":330037,"uid":108386,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T00:30:17.000Z","msg":"大陸野關我咩事"},{"pid":"52d7ec5510728104cf217546251300d7c6cffd0e","tid":330037,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedB